OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA spell of persistent rain
OL,6,Fspreads across the region during the
OL,7,Fmorning, followed by sunny spells and
OL,8,Fscattered showers in the afternoon.
OL,9,FThese could prove locally heavy with a
OL,10,Frisk of hail and thunder. Turning
OL,11,Fincreasingly windy through the day.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FFurther showers or longer
OL,14,Fspells of rain likely into the evening
OL,15,Fand overnight. Remaining rather
OL,16,Fbreezy, particularly near coasts and
OL,17,Fover the hills.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
