OL,2,W+.-'"-$/*%*%*%/"-$/*%Q,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CThursday:FRemaining breezy on Thursday
OL,6,Fwith sunny spells and showers, however
OL,7,Fthese merging at times to give longer
OL,8,Fspells of rain. Near normal
OL,9,Ftemperatures.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FShowers
OL,12,Fless frequent on Friday. A spell of
OL,13,Frain and stronger winds arriving
OL,14,FSaturday, with showers or longer
OL,15,Fspells of rain on Sunday. Temperatures
OL,16,Fclose to or slightly below normal.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
